## Additional Terms for GreenBit Recycling Platform

### About This Project

GreenBit is a web-based platform designed to facilitate recycling and waste management
by connecting recyclers with collection points and managing recycling requests.

### Environmental Commitment

This software is created with the intention of promoting environmental sustainability
and responsible waste management practices. Users are encouraged to use this platform
to support recycling initiatives and environmental conservation efforts.

### Educational Use

This project may be used for educational purposes, research, and non-commercial
environmental initiatives without restriction, in accordance with the MIT License terms above.

### Commercial Use

Commercial use is permitted under the MIT License. However, we encourage commercial
users to contribute back to environmental causes and open-source development.

### Contribution Guidelines

- Contributions that improve environmental impact tracking are especially welcome
- Please ensure any modifications maintain the platform's focus on sustainability
- Follow existing code standards and documentation practices

### Disclaimer

While this software is designed to support recycling efforts, users are responsible
for ensuring compliance with local environmental regulations and waste management laws.

